pokedexEntries.red: If interrupted while it is miming, it will slap around the offender with its broad hands.
pokedexEntries.blue: If interrupted while it is miming, it will slap around the offender with its broad hands.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Always practices its pantomime act. It makes enemies believe something exists that really doesn't.
pokedexEntries.gold: A skilled mime from birth, it gains the ability to create invisible objects as it matures.
pokedexEntries.silver: Its fingertips emit a peculiar force field that hardens air to create an actual wall.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It uses the mysterious power it has in its fingers to solidify air into an invisible wall.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once it is believed, it will exist as if it were a real thing.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once it is believed, it will exist as if it were a real thing.
pokedexEntries.emerald: A Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. It can convince others that something unseeable actually exists. Once believed, the imaginary object does become real.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It is adept at conning people. It is said to be able to create walls out of thin air by miming.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: If interrupted while it is miming, it will suddenly DoubleSlap the offender with its broad hands.
pokedexEntries.diamond: It is a pantomime expert that can create invisible but solid walls using miming gestures.
pokedexEntries.pearl: Emanations from its fingertips solidify the air into invisible walls that repel even harsh attacks.
pokedexEntries.platinum: It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: A skilled mime from birth, it gains the ability to create invisible objects as it matures.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Its fingertips emit a peculiar force field that hardens air to create an actual wall.
pokedexEntries.black: It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air.
pokedexEntries.white: It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air.
pokedexEntries.black2: It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air.
pokedexEntries.white2: It shapes an invisible wall in midair by minutely vibrating its fingertips to stop molecules in the air.
pokedexEntries.x: Emanations from its fingertips solidify the air into invisible walls that repel even harsh attacks.
pokedexEntries.y: It is adept at conning people. It is said to be able to create walls out of thin air by miming.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once the watchers are convinced, the unseeable thing exists as if it were real.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once the watchers are convinced, the unseeable thing exists as if it were real.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: Its pantomime skills are wonderful. You may become enraptured while watching it, but next thing you know, Mr. Mime has made a real wall.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: It creates invisible walls with its pantomiming. If you don’t act impressed, it will attack you with a double slap!
